# Lady Vidanya (Anya Lyre) Lorridan d'Sivis

Affiliation: House Sivis
Description: As indicated by her name, Anya is the great-grand-daughter of Doyenne Lysse Lorridan d'Sivis, ruler of House Sivis's ruling council. Anya is a Chronicler, a journalist working specifically for the prestigious Korranberg Chronicle.
Location: Aundair, Fairhaven
Race: Gnome
Role: Chronicler, Information broker
Status: Alive